parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "EGNN",
  "software_requirements": [
    "ncf/1.0.0-fasrc01",
    "miniconda3/py310_22.11.1-1-linux_x64-ncf",
    "cuda/12.2.0-fasrc01",
    "conda environment 'ten'"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "cores": 8,
    "runtime": "0-60:00",
    "partition": "gpu",
    "gpu": "nvidia_a100-sxm4-80gb:1",
    "memory": "32000"
  },
  "script_details": {
    "python_script": "src/main_qm9.py",
    "arguments": {
      "lifters": "atom:0 bond:1 functional_group:2 ring:2 supercell:3",
      "target_name": "$TARGET_NAME",
      "connectivity": "self_and_neighbors",
      "visible_dims": "0 1 2 3",
      "neighbor_types": "+1 -1 max",
      "epochs": 1000,
      "batch_size": 96,
      "weight_decay": "1e-16",
      "lr": "$LR",
      "num_layers": 7,
      "num_hidden": 128,
      "model_name": "ten",
      "dim": 3,
      "splits": "egnn",
      "clip_gradient": "--clip_gradient" if "$CLIP_GRADIENT" == "True" else ""
    }
  }
}
```
